title: When will I get my ranked rewards??
body: So the 2016 ranked season finished and I was in silver IV and I still haven't got my ranked rewards.I was wondering will I even get them and if I get them when will it be.

replies.body: Ranked Rewards have already gone out, so I recommend reaching out in a [**support ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) where we'll be able to take a look at what's going on.

I've had the same problem. I remember last season I had a similar issue, and I got my rewards literally at the very end after the true reset. I don't know why it takes longer for some accounts than others.
